name: Portrait of a Psycho
description:
Portrait of a psycho This is a portrait
of a psycho. An unstable monster, he
thrives in others' misery and enjoys
carnage. Oddyn intensifies strongly
from it! 3d animation made in
Houdini, rendered using Redshift
1500*1500 My first electro mix to my
artwork ever. Hope you enjoy it! I
found the samples on freesound.org
and played around with it for this
portrait of my buddy Oddyn.
